# Reporting system

## Charts (`components/reports/ReportsCharts.tsx`)

- Billable vs non-billable pie: `label={false}` on `<Pie>` so labels do not overlap the legend; tune `PieChart` margins; `Legend` `verticalAlign="bottom"`; add `paddingTop` on the wrapper as needed.

When extending exports or filters, align with existing `lib/reports/*` patterns and manager API routes under `app/api/manager/reports/**`.
